OOC: Hey, thanks for the idea there Cyberwolf.

DIAMOND::

She stopped and looked around her room.  She closed her eyes and felt her 
skin start to tingle.  She felt the outside of her skin start to harden.  
Her eyes were glazed over as the scales changed from her normal scales to 
those about to be shed.  She smiled and then with one quick movement, she 
slit the top scales on her head with her claw and pulled the old skin off 
her body.  She stepped out of the skin and stood there, a renewed snake. Her 
new scales were jet black, soft and supple, shiny and seductive.  She went 
to the mirror and looked at her new scales. "Hsssssss, I like thisss new 
ssskin. Perhapsss the othersss will admire it asss much asss I." And with 
that, she left her room and went to the main communications room.
